{"tid":2397641,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我俾班主任揾人打我，道歉plz","createTime":"2021-02-06T15:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T17:04:40.000Z","uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"058b45188950aeaa9f072ef9d2b938a23cee71f1","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"plz"},{"pid":"31df7016b018067930a6b0ba7e7a0adab92e58a4","tid":2397641,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"十倍奉還"},{"pid":"d7682cabdf4351c50613a7c7a1d77ca11962e6be","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HdkSbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HdkSbB.jpg&h=9746442e&s={SIZE}\" /> plz 唔好打我。打左就道歉，賠番7日時間同醫藥費，其他精神創傷 仲有名譽受損 。當冇事。但7日時間，同住院費用冇理由要我承受家麻，大佬，我真的不認識甚麼人。"},{"pid":"5f466d7ecfa02f7f59632f766b883d8c14e9daa1","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31df7016b018067930a6b0ba7e7a0adab92e58a4","tid":2397641,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"十倍奉還"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:09:48.000Z","msg":"咁佢打左我一鑊，佢除左爽之外就冇其他得着，相反我俾你打，損失好大的嘛"},{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed3ad6e20ff60fdbb09250a932e43262451e0c9d","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"睇左啦，醫生冇同我講野 之後徐敏玲入左間房，個醫生叫我出去，唔知佢響入面點屈我。之後就咩消息都冇。之後佢叫我<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">躝</span></span>"},{"pid":"47362e98dfac51bf2a4058804d83ffd015efb4d6","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"因為佢想省我時間，打擊我。香港人多資源少，所以啲人都好想整死其他人，依個係天性黎。"},{"pid":"ffbed47aa068774b2d61f5a56c21aae29f5acf7c","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"佢目的係想晒我時間，嚇到我傻，搞死啲基層學生，而自己就賺錢錢。順便通過打鳩人獲得成功感。"},{"pid":"502c5b06a01320fb652dafb40d4279e548de895d","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"仲有討回公道，點討，討一江春水向東流。基層地獄。"},{"pid":"0dcf0f59a3271c3e65541df00d5320c2fa59b31e","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"假如我行過去，要佢give me my money。佢一定唔認，之後再揾好多人再圍多我幾鑊。話唔定啲中學生仲會想打柒我添。想來十分驚。"},{"pid":"ed8af3c53d65de48dfcff4a82de8307e29d99e20","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:11:34.000Z","msg":"賠番我的童年時光給我plz"},{"pid":"d91ece833bccb967215d5f2272b04e56fe7ad177","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"讀書時間，童年時光。"},{"pid":"b8aee7f5e3a00c2893916fc5728310edb259760e","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"睇醫生到底對我俾人打怎會有幫助？分分鐘俾人打得仲大力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13cfaa9388ca97e63d2296c5e40a6bd8059a761","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"佢俾左啲藥我，我偷偷地扔左。因為關鍵係對方想我死。我點解要因為對方想我死就俾佢控制。。。"},{"pid":"5808c3845cf80377885ccabc1176c26dd010f910","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"佢將我打成殘廢，仲叫我食藥。我一定要扔左佢。因為人人都明白的。"},{"pid":"523eaa39acb57c4c0676494e8ee4339f6c0dc380","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"佢特登將我打殘，再叫我食藥。白痴先會食吧。明明一開始冇俾人打就唔會受傷。。。。"},{"pid":"003e55d29a7220bc04f0240a565be0cb3073f023","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"我俾人打，醫生係幫唔到我架，佢又唔係保鏢。。。。。。"},{"pid":"adb37ae22125e7264eb5abf1749b294f0e13e2e0","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"仲有，我響果度，係咩都唔做，就會俾人打。我點控制其他隻手，佢就係想打鳩我。我點睇醫生，佢都會打鳩我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976269fdd9f20b13be9244781fb98bfe8b958456","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48626c0b23919fb47317233e6e7302c2b14764","tid":2397641,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"個問題原因∶因為香港人天生想其他人死，要搶奪資源，要批鬥别人。醫生係醫唔好的。。。。。"},{"pid":"5dee4d68e0311a8efe72e6fbed177452c94ce743","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"善良me的tragedy。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85abc34db3d9e7a2f9018620655890ac3a222e0","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"我太善良了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1792bdc19ccd265cbaf6d1c7d04ca4bf076ff9","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"我太善良，唔識搶奪資源，唔識批鬥别人，所以小時候俾人打。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvWbeW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvWbeW1.jpg&h=733cee38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4f1f2051bbc437cdbb76302e7e0f5644eddd03","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"我天生就唔識搶資源同批鬥人，以後都唔會識。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQ6nmCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQ6nmCo.jpg&h=9052068a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d99439aeb1a392c5cec8ae4e5b84244b77dd57a4","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"真係想幫那個時候的me。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講出真相最實用。真係想一個人好，應該由細開始就叫佢「小心啲，出面世界啲人好恐怖，會想盡方法搞死」<br />\n想你死想你死<br />\n你要小心啲<br />\n啲人想你死，<br />\n明唔明"},{"pid":"b7a58b2bde415cced55b4986c0b591eedb0e7b86","tid":2397641,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"你真係想幫人，就要俾佢知道真相。「人人都想你死，你要小鳩心啲，隨時都會有人想你死，想搶你錢，想打柒你，你個仆街，你小心，你死緊！你最好欣住，扑你個街，屌！你小心啲！」咁先係最好嘅醫生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}